Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.37,messageinthepass,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀哈哈哈～哈 小后——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.37,messageinthepass,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的伞是不是忘在你那～～啦？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.37,messageinthepass,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有！没有——
